[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
A dry wind blows through. Mixed with it is the heat of the sun and the earth. And the smell of people, animals and plants. [l][r]
[r]It's completely different from the wind in that world, which is just cold. But in the end, they may be the same. [l][r]
[r]The sun shone just as it did in that world. It shone on the two of them just like it did in that world. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
Laughter echoes throughout the city. [l][r]
[r]It's the laughter of the girl who was once the happiest in the world, and the girl who was once the most unhappy in the world. [l][r]
[r]The two voices blended together, enveloping each other and those around them in a modest happiness, and continued to echo forever beyond the crowd. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

